bcl:definition.bcl:text:
determination date means, in respect of any calculation of interest
that is to be added to or that has accrued on a foreign money judgment, the date on which
that calculation is made;

bcl:paragraph.bcl:text:
if paragraph (a) does not apply, the rate that is, before the determination
            date, published in the Table as being the rate applicable to the currency jurisdiction
            for the calendar quarter in which the calendar month falls;

if paragraphs (a) and (b) do not apply, the rate that is, before the
            determination date, published in the Table as being the rate applicable to the currency
            jurisdiction for the calendar year in which the calendar month falls;
